Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春天的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約瑟夫 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約瑟夫真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 約瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了麼 聽到了吧 樅樹在唱歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂 約瑟夫 不要在玩了 該吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 約瑟夫 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行 要先去洗洗手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 雪融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 有花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約瑟夫 快看 雪下邊有朵花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香啊 有泥土的芳香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約瑟夫 快過來 你也聞聞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好聞 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 也讓爺爺來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺 爺爺 快來 快過來 快來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要問了 快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 雪下邊開了一朵可愛的花兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是雪歌草
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪歌草？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 春天快來時 它就會在雪地裡發芽\N在梗的前端開出美麗的花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是春天來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這朵花是在告訴我們春天來了啊\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺 是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪崩\N雪崩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 這幾天天氣很好 山上的雪開始融化\N從山上往下掉了 那也是春天到來的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是雪崩很危險的 被捲入就再也出不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 我們去吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春天了 春天來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完飯再出去\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 約瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是雪歌草麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得\N早上好 海蒂 一起去滑雪橇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你把花摘了 為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?\N我說雪歌草
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個啊　不是我摘的　是約瑟夫在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 約瑟夫 是你摘的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 把花給我吧\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 都已經折斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大將軍 肚子餓不餓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:09:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 爺爺 飯剛剛吃過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好吃的肉乾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 肉乾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進屋來吃點吧\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 雪歌草開了就說明春天就要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽 外邊的聲音 那也說明春天來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都沒在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上不是吃過飯了麼\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?\N在這停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡等我一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 你怎麼摘下來了 剛剛還對我發火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要用這朵花 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真任性啊 隨便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 海蒂來了\N啊 是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 阿姨\N您好 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎你來 海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 送您的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是雪歌草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 味道很好聞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很香 春天的氣味 春天來了 布莉緹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 是春天的氣味 海蒂把春天的氣味帶給我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春天真的是到了 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了吧 海蒂 快走吧\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 我還會再來的 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂真是個善良的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的 海蒂不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能行的 就是用腳來轉彎 刹車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 你來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 交給我吧 出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海 海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右轉 快右轉\N右轉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能行的 再讓我試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險 危險 都說危險啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 我很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停 快點停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂 不要在玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是她啊 她就海蒂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是海蒂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 是不是都回答一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是海蒂吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是又怎麼樣 你有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在包庇她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 你和女孩子一起玩 會變的和女孩子一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒這回事\N就是 才沒這回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在說這些奇怪的話 快點道歉 快道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這孩子在 突然就神氣起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說了 快點道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我們道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過要和我們比雪橇 你們贏了才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 比就比
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那就雙人賽 我們倆一組 你們倆一組\N哎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢比了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比就比 我們比 你們要是輸了就得道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老頭子的孫女氣勢倒是很足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 開始比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾 不許推
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也推就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到村子的廣場是終點\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數到三就開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊了哦\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超過了 超過你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會輸給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領先了 領先了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終點要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們贏了 萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂\N彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒受傷吧 海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的\N太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不甘心的話 我們隨時奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們居然跑到村子附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩?\N我是說小雪它們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪家在哪裡？彼得 我們去看它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 現在麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能帶你去看羊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點回去吧 不然你爺爺生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 要下雨了 快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經開始下了 去樹林裡走吧
